title: Tuesday Post Show (01-04-21)
itunes:title: Tuesday Post Show (01-04-21)
description:
Bobby starts out by saying he crashed energy wise as soon as we started this post show. He shares a story about a guy who gets bumped to first class on flights because he is over 7ft tall. Eddie wants to know what everyone’s favorite Christmas present was…so we each share ours. Bobby shares his experience “floating” in salt water that he got as a gift. Bobby shares a story about his Christmas party he had at his house. Phone Screener Abby reveals she said she had COVID over break. Bobby also addresses a pregnancy rumor that happened over the break.
